headline: RBC Maintains Neutral View on Conagra (CAG) as Q4 Miss Highlights Growth Pressures
summary: Conagra Brands Inc. (NYSE:CAG) is one of the most oversold S&P 500 stocks so far in 2025. The stock has declined around 30%–32% both YTD and over the past year, largely reflecting broader consumer weakness and persistent inflation, which continue to cloud the outlook for packaged food companies. headline: Bear of the Day: General Mills (GIS)
summary: General Mills faces headwinds from evolving consumer preferences amid the "MAHA" movement. To regain momentum, GIS will need to spend millions in R&D to adapt its product portfolio.
